Package magellan.library.utils

Interface Taggable

  • All Known Subinterfaces:
    Building, Faction, Group, Region, Ship, TempUnit, Unit, UnitContainer, ZeroUnit
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    MagellanBuildingImpl, MagellanFactionImpl, MagellanGroupImpl, MagellanRegionImpl, MagellanShipImpl, MagellanTempUnitImpl, MagellanUnitContainerImpl, MagellanUnitImpl, MagellanZeroUnitImpl
    public interface Taggable
    A Taggable object works much like a Map. Use it for for assigning additional tags to report objects which are not official tags.
    Version:
    1.0
    Author:
    Andreas
